
Rubygems setup
    install ruby
    download tgz from https://rubygems.org/pages/download
    ruby setup.rb --destdir = (root of /usr/bin).  
    gem executable in <dest dir>/usr/bin.  Move to ~/bin
    gem install <gem name>.  Gem executable in ~/.bin

Install gems:
gem install --user-dir -V tumuxinator

Uninstall all 
sudo gem uninstall -i /usr/local/share/gems --all

statement modifiers
	puts 'Somethign' if condition == true
	square = val*val while val < 1000

arrays
	make w/o quoting values
		a = %w( ant bee cat dog elk )

regex
	~= match operator

code blocks
	code between braces {} or 'do' & 'end'
	|<val>| in block is argument name
	

iterators
	methods that return successive elements from a collection
		['dog','cat'].each { |pet| puts pet }

files
	read from stdin
		line = gets
		gets also stores line in $_
	
